resources TNA(24)
notes
This is a TNA experiment to be co-ordinated with the ALIS (Auroral Large Imaging
System) experiment, located in Kiruna, Sweden.
The system should run a high resolution code such as arc1.

The experiment requires optically clear conditions and is thus overbooked.
